&lt;li&gt;Comfortable partnering with software engineers to productionize research and experimental work, not just deliver a one-off analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rigorous approach to experimentation: clear hypotheses, real statistical grounding, and results that hold up under scrutiny&lt;/li&gt;
